resources.name: Detailed information on public opinion website

description:
The interviews were conducted between the 20/10/2003 and the 05/11/2003. Both reports 150 (The quality of services) and 150b (eating a unique number for blocking credit cards) are drafted based on the volumes called "FL 150".

#####The results by volumes are distributed as follows:
* Volume A: Countries
* Volume AA: Groups of countries
* Volume A' (AP): Trends
* Volume AA' (AAP): Trends of groups of countries
* Volume B: EU/socio-demographics
* Volume C: Country/socio-demographics
title: Flash Eurobarometer 150: The quality of services / Creating a unique number for blocking credit cards (b)
name: S324_150
